Love Laws & Outlaws: Indoo Seth

Love Laws & Outlaws: Indoo Seth
A love story of a couple hailed from an orthodox society with lots of restrictions and how they overcome from all the trials and tribulations thrown on them. Their depth of love, their affection and care towards each other took them to the next level of love. The story tells you how a small chaos moved to a lovely date and then to a long relationship called marriage which changed their lives.
